            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CodexMate 0.0.5

- Improved command approval fallback handling so pending `exec_command` approvals show the correct waiting state more reliably.
- Added launch options and first-run behavior that make the packaged app easier to spot in UTM and other VM setups.
- Refined shortcut recording, resource loading, and packaging so local builds and signed app bundles behave more predictably.
]]></description>
